text: Pfäffikon can mean: *Pfäffikon (district), Canton of Zürich, Switzerland **Pfäffikon, Zürich (Pfäffikon ZH), a municipality and capital of the district *Pfäffikon, Schwyz (Pfäffikon SZ), a town within the municipality of Freienbach, Canton of Schwyz, Switzerland == Other == *Pfeffikon (Pfeffikon LU), a municipality in the canton of Lucerne, Switzerland
title: Pfäffikon
